    "title": "How Soulslike Combat Works: A Complete Guide",
    "seoTitle": "How Soulslike Combat Works: Complete Guide | Gaming Hub",
    "metaDescription": "Learn how soulslike combat works, from stamina management and dodge timing to parrying and boss patterns. Master the core mechanics that define the genre.",
    "category": "game-mechanics",
    "datePublished": "2024-05-10",
